name: Tomaco Sunderland Style by YeiyeiArt
description:
Hello guys!! after a while I bring a new style model. REMEMBER to follow the social networks and ask for your own models (ง͡ ¬᎑¬)ว I had this style in mind for a while since it is very stylized and beautiful. It combines a bit of cartoon style with a toon effect that gives the artist their particular touch. Perfect for stylizing your characters or experimenting with them (ノo)ノ I recommend using it with high forces “<1.0 - 0.8>” but you can try. Yeiyei out :D

⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️

Don’t forget to check out my other Disney Series Loras on my profile. Currently Rapunzel, Snow White, Merida, Cinderella, Pocahontas, Fa Mulan, Elsa, Anna, Tiana and Alice in Wonderland, Ariel, Aurora, Jasmine From the Princess Series ;D” Also u have The Bonus Series with: Nani Pelekai, Lifeguard (lilo & stitch). And Tinker bell, Jane Porter (Tarzan), Kida (atlantis), Chel.

Restaurant Series: Ronald McDonald, Wendys

Don’t forget to check out my other Disney Series Loras on my profile. YeiYeiArt.

Or

THE NEW !! Villain Collection: Maleficent, Ursula.
